<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">I&#x27;m not sure whether Microsoft Copilot and ChatGPT use different system prompts or if there&#x27;s something else behind it, but Copilot tends to have this overly cautious, sterile tone. It always seems to err on the side of safety, whereas ChatGPT generally just does what you ask as long as it&#x27;s reasonable.<p>So it often comes down to this choice:
